name: Shawn Porter
text: Good sandwich shop, nice and friendly people.

name: Josh Berger
text: The sandwiches here are fantastic. A little pricey, but what do you expect from a place like this? It's so much better quality than getting a premade sub at a 7/11. A large is the size of an adult's arm and is around $9. Can't do much better than that.

name: Mark Sutherland
text: They still make a very good sandwich after all this time I love the number 9

name: Jason Hagan
text: I had a great overall experience here. The manager was friendly and helpful, and had our order ready in minutes. The restaurant was clean and orderly. Highly recommend!

name: Felix Rivera
text: Great people working there very nice love their sadwiches

name: Sadie Love
text: Delicious meal and super fast service

name: Margaret Dowd
text: Got thanksgiving  day  wrap oh my get one you  won't be disappointed

name: Bill Peterson
text: The newer menu items (new to me) are delicious. I haven't been to one in a long time and I am glad I stopped back in.
